# Server Boundaries

- Keep SQLite SQL inside `src/lib/server/repository/`; routes and Svelte components should call repository methods.
- Add schema changes in `repository/schema.ts`, public methods in `repository/index.ts`, row conversion in `repository/mappers.ts`, and domain SQL in the matching repository module.
- Do not log SMTP passwords, OAuth refresh tokens, AI API keys, admin password hashes, session tokens, or decrypted app secrets.
- Preserve the campaign send-once invariant from `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`.
- Shared server helpers belong in `src/lib/server` when behavior is reused, security-sensitive, background-capable, or useful to test directly.
- If a change touches sending or communications, use the `scuba-send-safety` skill.
